flowchart LR
    Client([Client])

    Client -->|Command\ncreate / update / delete| CH[Command Handler]
    Client -->|Query\nread request| QH[Query Handler]

    CH --> Validate{Validate\nCommand}
    Validate -->|Invalid| Reject[Return Error\nto Client]
    Validate -->|Valid| WriteStore[(Write Store\nNormalized DB)]
    WriteStore --> Event[Domain Event\nPublished]
    Event --> Bus[[Event Bus]]
    Bus --> Projector[Event Projector]
    Projector --> ReadStore[(Read Store\nDenormalized\nProjection)]
    QH --> ReadStore
